[src:aws-config/provisioning-technology] The network operator typically sends these settings to the subscriber's handset using SMS text services or HTML, and less commonly WAP, depending on what the mobile operating systems can accept.
[src:aws-config/provisioning-technology] A general example of provisioning is with data services.
